comments: Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with George's (LAC) hand before making clean contact with the ball thereafter on the driving shot attempt.
As Fox's (SAC) momentum carries him toward the baseline, George (LAC) makes marginal contact as he releases from Fox at the end of his drive.
Huerter (SAC) touches the ball, which has a chance to score, above rim level after it has hit the backboard.
Although Covington (LAC) jumps vertically and absorbs the body contact, he brings his arm down and makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm, affecting his shot attempt.
Powell (LAC) makes marginal contact with Sabonis (SAC) after Sabonis retrieves the rebound. The contact does not affect his ability to pass.
Sabonis (SAC) is retreating in George's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact in his chest during the drive.
George (LAC) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before passing.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: George (LAC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
George (LAC) jumps and turns into Fox's (SAC) lower body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) and Covington (LAC) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

Murray (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball to block the shot prior to marginal contact occurring with Powell's (LAC) head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Batum (LAC) dislodges Barnes (SAC) from his position during the rebound, affecting his ability to retrieve the ball.
George (LAC) does not establish himself in Barnes' (SAC) path as he is still moving laterally when contact occurs on the driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Fox (SAC) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Powell?s (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) briefly grasps and releases Jackson's (LAC) off-arm on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Fox (SAC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Huerter (SAC) commits take foul on George (LAC).
Huerter (SAC) commits a take foul on Powell (LAC).
